## 請求驗證規則

### 輸入驗證
```php
class InputValidator {
    public function validateRoomId($roomId) {
        return preg_match('/^room_[a-zA-Z0-9_]+$/', $roomId);
    }
    
    public function validateUserId($userId) {
        return preg_match('/^[a-zA-Z0-9_]{3,20}$/', $userId);
    }
    
    public function validateCode($code) {
        return strlen($code) <= 10000 && mb_check_encoding($code, 'UTF-8');
    }
    
    public function sanitizeInput($input) {
        return htmlspecialchars(trim($input), ENT_QUOTES, 'UTF-8');
    }
}
```

### 參數檢查
```php
function validateRequiredParams($params, $required) {
    foreach ($required as $param) {
        if (!isset($params[$param]) || empty($params[$param])) {
            throw new InvalidArgumentException("缺少必要參數: $param");
        }
    }
}
```

