## 性能監控

### API性能記錄
```php
class APIMonitor {
    public function recordRequest($endpoint, $method, $responseTime, $statusCode) {
        $logData = [
            'endpoint' => $endpoint,
            'method' => $method,
            'response_time' => $responseTime,
            'status_code' => $statusCode,
            'timestamp' => date('c'),
            'memory_usage' => memory_get_peak_usage(true)
        ];
        
        $this->logger->info('API Request', $logData);
    }
    
    public function getPerformanceStats($timeRange = '1h') {
        return [
            'total_requests' => $this->getTotalRequests($timeRange),
            'average_response_time' => $this->getAverageResponseTime($timeRange),
            'error_rate' => $this->getErrorRate($timeRange),
            'top_endpoints' => $this->getTopEndpoints($timeRange)
        ];
    }
}
```

## 測試規範

### API測試用例
```php
class APITest {
    public function testCodeSaveAPI() {
        $response = $this->post('/api/code.php', [
            'action' => 'save',
            'room_id' => 'test_room',
            'code' => 'print("Hello World")'
        ]);
        
        $this->assertEquals(200, $response->getStatusCode());
        $this->assertTrue($response->json()['success']);
    }
    
    public function testInvalidParameters() {
        $response = $this->post('/api/code.php', [
            'action' => 'save'
            // 缺少必要參數
        ]);
        
        $this->assertEquals(400, $response->getStatusCode());
        $this->assertFalse($response->json()['success']);
    }
}
```

